<bibRefCitation author="Remes Lenicov, A. M. &amp; Paradell, S. L." box="[324,708,1929,1956]" pageId="54" pageNumber="55" pagination="263 - 269" refId="ref81130" refString="Remes Lenicov, A. M. &amp; Paradell, S. L. (2009) Argentinean species of the Faltala leafhopper group (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Deltocephalinae). Revista de la Sociedad Entomologica Argentina, 68, 263 - 269." type="journal article" year="2009">Remes Lenicov &amp; Paradell (2009)</bibRefCitation>
